Certainly! Here is the code for the `Solution` class shown in the image:

```python
class Solution:
    def hasCycle(self, head: ListNode) -> bool:
        slow, fast = head, head

        while fast and fast.next:
            slow = slow.next
            fast = fast.next.next
            if slow == fast:
                return True

        return False
